Carlosio Toro worked as a member of the Medellin Cartel in the 1980s . 
  He fled Colombia fearing for his life and came to the US as an informant for the DEA . 
  Toro was one of the DEA's strongest assets and helped carry out undercover stings . 
  He was told he would be rewarded with US citizenship but retired after declining health . 
  He is now facing deportation from the US and says he will be killed if he is sent back . 
 